            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and <strong>pepper strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
