            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add your <strong>beluga lentils</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
