      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>creamy single soy</strong> to the pan and bring to a boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 10-12 min, stirring regularly, until the sauce has thickened to a risotto-like consistency – this is your <strong>plant-based tomato beluga lentil risotto</strong></p>",
